    "content": "Song: Everybody, Everybody\r\nAlbum: Dreamland\r\nArtist: Black Box\r\n\r\nI love this song, and it's really jammin to play along with on bass, enjoy!\r\n\r\nThis song is in standard tuning (E, A, D, G)\r\n\r\nThe bass comes in at 0:16\r\n\r\n[tab]G-----------------------3----------1-3----------------------------|\r\nD-----3--1h3h1h3-----------1h3h1h3--------------------------------|\r\nA----------------3-2-1--------------------------------------------|\r\nE--1--------------------------------------------------------------| 3x[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA-----------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nE--1--------------------------------------------------------------| 1x[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G-----------------------3----------1-3----------------------------|\r\nD-----3--1h3h1h3-----------1h3h1h3--------------------------------|\r\nA----------------3-2-1--------------------------------------------|\r\nE--1--------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nThe last bar repeats until the end\r\n\r\nTabbed by Max Dietz",
